<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOOD DONATIONS BRIGHTEN DAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Thank you Laguna Hills! 
</P>
<P>
 In the 13 years I've been a letter carrier here, I've never enjoyed my job as 
much as I did on Saturday, May 14. 
</P>
<P>
 On that day I saw firsthand the generosity you people showed by leaving your 
non-perishable goods at your mailbox. 
</P>
<P>
 In our office alone, I saw large hampers full of food, at least enough to fill 
a large semitrailer. And that's just our office! 
</P>
<P>
 Imagine how much food was donated to our food banks in our communities from 
Long Beach to San Clemente. 
</P>
<P>
 I've never seen such teamwork. What a major accomplishment! 
</P>
<P>
 DENNIS STEWLOW 
</P>
<P>
 Laguna Hills 
</P>
