<P>
MORE COVERAGE NEEDED ON COUNTY SUPERVISOR RACE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * I am disappointed there has not been more coverage of the 3rd District 
county supervisor election in your newspaper. 
</P>
<P>
 Four years ago, The Times endorsed Don Wallace for supervisor. Where is the 
coverage of the June 7 election? I just know we will all soon be inundated with 
mail and glossy photos of what's-his-name telling what a great job he has done. 
Do you feel safe in Los Angeles? I don't feel safe, and I don't want the county 
of Los Angeles turning into the city of Los Angeles. 
</P>
<P>
 MARY ALTMANN 
</P>
<P>
 Agoura Hills 
