<HEADLINE>
<P>
OBITUARY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Siville, Raymond W., 64, of Oxnard, retired teacher for the Oxnard Union High 
School District.Ted Mayr Funeral Home, Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura County obituaries are published free of charge as a public service to 
readers. Obituaries are based on information provided by mortuaries. 
</P>
