<TEXT>
<P>
 Cal State Fullerton distance runner Mike Tansley ran the 3,000-meter 
steeplechase in 8 minutes 52.53 seconds on Saturday at the Adidas Oregon Track 
Classic, putting himself "on the bubble" for qualifying for the NCAA 
championships, Titan Coach John Elders said. 
</P>
