<DOCID> 044352 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 22, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Magazine; Page 14; Magazine Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
