7,248 14.4% $181 $175 -3.3% Orange County 2,506 3,313 32.2% $199 $198 -0.5% San 
Diego 2,753 3,072 11.6% $167 $169 1.2% Riverside 1,452 2,008 38.3% $130 $133 
2.3% San Bernardino 1,545 1,739 12.6% $128 $125 -2.3% Ventura 866 998 15.2% 
$205 $192 -6.3% So. California 15,459 18,378 18.9% $173 $170 -1.7%  
</P>
