<TEXT>
<P>
 Quote attribution -- In Saturday's editions of The Times in a story about the 
killing of a bear on a residential street, portions of a quote appearing in the 
Highlights column were incorrectly attributed to 12-year-old Alex Sandoval. In 
fact, he said: "What's happening is we're driving the animals out of their 
habitats." 
</P>
</TEXT>
